{
  "stem": "13251.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] You know, he'd tease the hell out of me, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't know where to go with this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The way I discovered the family, actually, is when we came to Israel.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was three of us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were sent to a, actually, to a youth kibbutz school like, you know, for training, youth training.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A friend of ours, Natan.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He came on the same boat to Israel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He's from France, actually, but we, we kind of met on the boat, whatever, and we became very close friends.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we kind of stuck together, the three of us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when we were sent to this youth training kibbutz, we rebelled.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I mean, we came to Israel as pioneers, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We wanted to start building and everything else, so we refused, and we ran away, OK?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we went to the authorities, the-- you know, like, the, that handle new immigrants.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we said, no way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We don't want to go back to school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We finished school.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So reluctantly, they sent us to a kibbutz in the Negev, which is like the worst place you can send kids.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I think the reason they sent us over there instead of sending us into a cushy kibbutz that was established that we'll probably say, yuck, you know, and say that's not for me.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'll go back to school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Well, they were wrong, because we loved it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Now when was this? 19--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was is '59.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean '49, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A year after War of Independence.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went to this kibbutz, and we felt accepted.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we felt, you know-- we felt we were doing something, you know, significant and-- no, we loved it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were wrong about thinking that we'd chicken out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What were you doing?",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
